NAKED!!  ?  
While there are some decent bodies in this series, very few of them are Billie's.  It's not until Ep. 6(?) that we finally see her face and torso in the same shot (save for one very quick flash earlier).  And I can't recall that we see her again.  
Whatever.  She's very nice to look at even without constant nip shots.  Too bad the series rapidly turns into a bore. 

BTW, quality is okay but certainly not stunning.  The first season looks like it was shot by Bob Guccioni - very soft picture - anyway, so this may be all you need.  If not there is an HD torrent.
